        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Improve degraded usage rendering",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Prefer Claude web usage before CLI fallback in app-auto mode, so available web detail is not skipped in favor of the slower CLI path.\n- Keep Codex local token/cost usage visible when remote quota metrics are unavailable, and suppress misleading remote-unavailable copy in that degraded state.\n- Add regression coverage for Claude planner ordering and Codex menu rendering without quota metrics.\n\n## Test plan\n- `swift test --filter ClaudeSourcePlannerTests`\n- `swift test --filter ClaudeBaselineCharacterizationTests`\n- `swift test --filter ClaudeDebugDiagnosticsTests`\n- `swift test --filter MenuCardModelCodexProjectionTests`\n- `swift test --filter MenuCardModelCodexDegradedQuotaTests`\n- `swift test --filter UsageMenuCardLayoutTests`\n- `make check`\n\nRelated #1321\nRelated #1287\nRelated #1380\n\nMade with [Cursor](https://cursor.com)",
